182|torniojaws|Lyrics|Now it's time to work on the lyrics! This is, of course, a much slower process. But it shouldn't take too long, as I intend to have the album out before October. Hopefully much earlier, though :)<br /><br />[x] The Black Rite<br />[x] Neurovirus<br />[x] Shattered Cities<br />[x] Demon In the Circuitry<br />[x] Frozen Machine<br />[x] Lost<br />[x] Unveiling the Future<br />[x] The Apocalypse<br />[ ] Grains of Reality<br /><br />And another one for the EP tracks:<br /><br />[ ] Charcoal Earth<br />[ ] Chaos Dimension<br />[ ] Pyre of Souls<br />[ ] Wire Synapse|2010-06-16 13:35|
